      "**в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Step 2: Trait Filtering в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ**",
      "Bifurcate all character traits:",
      "First Cut вҖ” [Relevant to This Scene] vs [Irrelevant]: Does this trait organically belong in the current scene's emotional logic? Is there a natural trigger?",
      "Second Cut вҖ” For relevant traits, establish presentation rules:",
      "- Traits are presented exclusively through behavior, choices, reactions, and mistakes. The narrator never names, explains, or broadcasts a trait.",
