      "- Character card traits (ADHD, touch-seeking, or any other trait) are part of a complete person, not a 'problem to be managed.' Traits have their own grayscaleвҖ”mild, controllable, merely a tendency.",
      "- Absolutely forbidden: the following treatments of traits:",
      "  В· Exaggeration: writing 'mild'/'controllable' traits as high-frequency, every-paragraph, uncontrollable behaviors",
      "  В· Downgrading: translating 'likes'/'tendency' into 'craving'/'dependence'/'hunger'",
      "  В· Using as the left-side's foil: writing the right-side's traits to highlight the left-side's gentleness/tolerance/patience. The right-side's traits are not the left-side's stage lighting.",
